 metric standards for length and mass and established permanent mechanisms to}{\f1\fs22\insrsid6690497  }{\f1\fs22\insrsid4522937\charrsid4539373 recommend and adopt further }{\f1\fs22\insrsid150985 refinements}{\f1\fs22\insrsid4522937\charrsid4539373 
 in the metric system. This agreement, commonly}{\f1\fs22\insrsid6690497  }{\f1\fs22\insrsid4522937\charrsid4539373 called the "Treaty of the Meter" in the United States, was signed by 17 countries, including the}{\f1\fs22\insrsid6690497  }{
